Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 谷風可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷風機 瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不要拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦 長道
